To:

```python
from datetime import datetime, timedelta
...
if __name__ == '__main__':
    app.run(host='0.0.0.0', port=5000, debug=True)
```

This fix ensures that timedelta is available when creating the estimated delivery time in the checkout process, allowing the app to run without errors.

